Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:31.48,倒數,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 居然能和FD的起跑不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉先生的Levin果然厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我的Levin也裝上了Turbo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可級別沒得比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的Levin 現在改用Super Charged了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Charged？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的引擎結果還是報廢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.48,0:24:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸給樹的朋友 讓他非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.10,0:24:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是傾盡全力去跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.66,0:24:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…Super Charged還眞有點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.94,0:24:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 像86這樣的車…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Super Charged很配
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.82,0:24:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥非常滿足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說比起以前的Turbo 更具戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.72,0:24:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到達前面的中低速路段
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.37,0:24:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有多少馬力 也不能完全發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.34,0:24:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是車手對車手的勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.15,0:24:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公路戰 是意志堅強的一方取勝！
